27688.title: FTS-Euro versus WFTDA Rank (Oct 2018)
27688.content: FTS-Euro versus WFTDA Rank (Oct 2018). Chart compares the top teams ranked by FTS-Euro and WFTDA-Rank, and shows that there are several differences in ordering, some crossing SFC tier boundaries.

27689.title: Graph of WFTDA Rank v FTS-Euro Rank
27689.content: Scatter-chart showing WFTDA-Rank (Y axis) versus FTS-Euro Rank (X axis) for all WFTDA-ranked teams. The graph is clearly correlated, but has a lot of spread and several outliers.
